{
  "chapter": 115,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为\"恶人再聚\"，十大恶人中的屠娇娇、白开心将轩辕三光带回龟山，与李大嘴、哈哈儿、杜杀重聚。轩辕三光坦白自己将十大恶人托李老实保管的黄金白银箱子全部输光并抛入扬子江，令众人震惊。随后众人讨论放走被囚的花无缺和铁心兰，白开心提议让二人成亲，哈哈儿附和要办喜事，屠娇娇则提议将白夫人也嫁给白开心。轩辕三光提出将慕容家的喜事一起办，众人计划闯入慕容家喜堂。白开心担心燕南天可能出现在喜宴上，屠娇娇分析江玉郎会将燕南天引开，人多之处反而安全。本章展现了十大恶人重聚后的互相嘲讽、尔虞我诈，以及他们对花无缺、铁心兰的处置决定。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早已知道燕南天必定要上他的当，我猜的果然不错。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小鬼果然有两下子，也难为他装得真他妈的像极了，燕南天居然真跟着他走，真是鬼迷了心窍。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这下子燕南天非但永远休想找得到小鱼儿，只怕连命也要送在这父子俩人的身上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我当是谁呢，原来是恶赌鬼到了，哈哈，久违久违。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "恶赌鬼，多年不见，怎地一见面你就爬到屠娇娇身上去了？难道你这赌鬼已变成了色鬼了么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们这些龟儿子全都到这里来了，龟山上有了你们这么多龟儿子，倒真的名副其实。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "屠娇娇莫名其妙地点了你七八处穴道，又像条狗似的将你掼在地上，你不找她拼命，反而开起玩笑来了，嘿嘿。看来你这人实在是好欺负得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "我问你，你这不男不女的龟儿子为什么要点老子的穴道，难道真当老子是好欺负的么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我问你，你方才冲出去是不是想去通风报讯，叫燕南天莫要上江别鹤父子的当？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕南天？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他……他的病已好了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他非但病已好了，而且功夫仿佛比以前更强，我见到他的人时，还没有认出他来，但见他露了一手功夫后，就知道必是燕南天无疑。因为除了燕南天之外，世上再也没有第二个人有那么高的武功。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他已被江别鹤父子骗走，但恶赌鬼却想将他找回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "老子不过是想要他将江别鹤父子宰了而已，并没有别的意思。老子难道还会要燕南天来找你们的麻烦不成？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我问你，你若没有做亏心事，为什么一见到我们就跑呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "这……这个……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你说呀！你怎地说不出话来了？这不是做贼心虚是什么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "老子又没有掘你祖坟，你龟儿子为什么找老子麻烦？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你方才是不是一见他们就跑？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "我，格老子，不错，我是跑了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因老子已将你们的钱都输光了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我们的钱？什么钱？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都知道老子是恶赌鬼，却不知老子虽喜欢赢钱，也喜欢输钱，只要有钱输，实在比赢钱更过瘾，尤其是输给那些没有钱的小赌鬼，看到他们赢钱后那种欢天喜地的模样，那其中的乐趣，你们这些龟儿子只怕永远也想像不到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前几个月，我替一个朋友将一票银子送回去给江南的大富翁段合肥，虽然因此得罪了江别鹤父子，却跟段合肥斗了半个月蟋蟀，赢了他几十万，我手头有了赌本，就想送出去一些了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "想不到你这恶赌鬼倒真是劫富济贫的侠盗。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "但是老子越是想输，那银子就偏偏跟老子作对，总是输不出去。有一天我正在一家菜馆里喝茶，旁边居然有人赌起骰子来了，我一看，正中下怀，就和那些龟儿子赌了起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你又赢了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "该当那些龟儿子走运，老子的赌运恰巧在那里走光了，别人掷出个四点，老子都赶不上，竟一连输了几天几夜。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "输得好。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那家茶馆在一条小巷里，老子输了三天后，那巷子里老老少少都赢了老子不少，只有个糟老头子，虽然每天都到这茶馆里来喝茶，每天都看到老子输，却硬是不动心，硬是不肯下场来赌一手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他越不肯赌，老子就越找他赌，别人都说这老头子非但不赌钱，而且不抽烟，不喝酒，是个标标准准的木头人，大家都叫他李老实，还说只要我能引得这李老实和我赌钱，他们每天就给我磕个头。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "想不到李家门里还有这么样的老好人，难得难得。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那条巷子里还有个屠寡妇，据说县里已快替她立贞节牌坊了，她虽在巷口摆了个小摊，但十年来来往往，就没有人看到她笑过，她家里也没有别的人，只有一条狗，替她看守门户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到屠家门里居然还有人肯守寡，难得难得，只不过可惜她还是养了一条狗……哈哈，狗最大的好处就是不会说话。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赌到第四天，我还剩下三万两银子，我就将银子全都堆到李老实面前，我说我只要说一个字，就能令那屠寡妇笑起来，再说一个字，就能叫她打我一个耳光，我问李老实信不信？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "他信不信？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "屠寡妇从来不笑的，男女授受不亲，寡妇更不能打男人的耳光，李老实自然不信，于是我就跟他打赌，我若输了，就将剩下的银子全都给他，我若赢了，只要他再陪我赌十把骰子。他望着面前的银子，足足望了半个多时辰，终于还是跟我赌了。他虽然老实，但老实人见到送上门来的银子，也舍不得不要的，只因每个人都认定我这场赌实是有输无赢，连半分机会都没有。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "但你却赢了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "只为了要跟他再赌个痛快，我自然非赢不可。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你是怎么样赢的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "只说一个字就能令寡妇发笑，再说个字就要她翻脸打人……这实在连我都被难住了。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了下午，那寡妇才摆起她那卖煎饼的摊子，那条狗和她寸步不离，自然也跟在她身旁，于是我就走过去，恭恭敬敬向那条狗磕了头，叫了声'爹'，那寡妇怔了怔，虽然想板起脸，终于还是忍不住笑了起来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人见到我果然只说了一个字，就令那寡妇发笑，虽然又佩服，又好笑，但还是想不出我怎能令她翻脸打我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "老实说，连我都想不出你会有什么法子。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过又跪到她面前，叫了她一声'妈'，她立刻就满脸通红，连脖子都粗了，狠狠打了我一耳光，转身就走。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "于是李老实只好陪我赌骰子，谁知我手气竟转了，一连赢了十场，开始时他还赌得很少，但到后来，他也输急了，竟将家里的夜壶、棉被都拿出来跟我赌，赌了十场后，他已输得干干净净，我就问他，你既然连赌本都没有了，还赌什么？他呆了半晌，忽然咬了牙，把我带到他家里去，他家里已被搬空了，但却还有个小屋子，里面堆着好几口大箱子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "大箱子？什么样的大箱子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "黑黝黝的大箱子，上面积满了尘土，李老实说，这本是别人托他看管的，他从来也没有碰过，但现在，他却顾不得这些了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人若是输急了，连老婆儿子都会押上赌桌的，这李老实虽然一生都很老实可靠，但老房子着火，烧得更快。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "他……他难道将那些箱子全都输给你了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "不错，可是我却未想到，那些箱子里竟装着全都是黄金白银，更未想到那些箱子竟是你们的，若非箱子里有你们的记号，我永远也不会想到你们竟会将箱子交给一个老头子保管，哈哈，这法子实在妙极。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却正如天上掉下了大元宝，平空落下了几百万，于是我就大赌特赌，到这里，已输得差不多了，剩下的已全都送别人作嫁妆。现在我已又是囊空如洗，你们要我还钱，我是一分也没有，要命倒有一条。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来……原来欧阳丁、欧阳当并没有将箱子藏在龟山，却存在李老实那里，我们还是上了他的当。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我们倒该感激这赌鬼才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "text": "感激他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "他若不说，我们就还要在这里作苦工，挖山洞，现在我们反倒可以休息休息了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实他并没有说错，若非轩辕三光，我们永远也不会知道箱子究竟在哪里？反而多费些事，多着些急。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "如此说来，你们不准备要他赔了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "他早已说过，要钱没有，要命一条……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "但他这身肉也不错，你难道不想尝尝味道么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "我若将这赌鬼吃进肚子里，那还得了，他若要我的肠子和胃打起赌来，我怎么吃得消？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你将银子都输光了，难道将箱子也输了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "箱子在哪里？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "老子嫌那些箱子太重，早已全都抛进扬子江了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "格老子，你龟儿子喜欢的是吃人肉，人肉却是银子买不到的，丢了几两银子，你难过什么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这你就不懂了，一个人年纪越大，就越贪财，我虽也知道那玩意儿吃不得，穿不得，也带不进棺材，但我却偏偏越来越喜欢它。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我每天什么都不干，只要让我关起门来数银子，我已经觉得很过瘾了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你们这些龟儿子只怕真的已经快进棺材了，一个人若是什么都不喜欢，只喜欢钱的话，他就已经死了大半截。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你们既然如此喜欢钱，为什么不再去偷，去抢？那些银子反正是你们这些龟儿子偷来抢来的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这你又不懂了，恶人也得有恶人的身份，像我们这样有身份的恶人，若再去杀人越货，岂不叫人笑掉大牙。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到你们这些龟儿子连强盗都不敢做了，你们还有什么用？我看你们不如屙泡尿自己淹死算了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "放你妈的屁，谁敢说'十大恶人'没有用？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "二十年前，你们也许可以算得上'十大恶人'，但在那乌龟洞里躲了二十年之后，你们已只能算是'五个缩头乌龟'了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你以为你是什么东西？就算在二十年前，你也没有资格称得上'十大恶人'，别人只不过是将你拿来凑数的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然我们都算不上是什么'恶人'，为什么不索性做件好事呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "做什么好事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "我们为什么不将这三个可怜虫放了，让他们感激一辈子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我们被人家恨了一辈子，偶尔也叫几个人感激我们，倒也不错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_du_sha",
      "text": "杜老大，你的意思怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "反正这三个人已离死不远，我杀他们也甚是无趣。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们既然要做好人，为什么不索性好人做到底？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "哈哈，损人不利己难道也做得出什么好事么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我坏事做了一辈子，如今也想尝尝做好事是什么滋味了，否则我死了到阎王爷那里去都不好交代。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你龟儿子究竟玩什么花样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这俩人你爱我，我爱你，已爱了好多年，只是中间多了个小鱼儿，现在小鱼儿既然已翘了辫子，我们为什么不索性将这两人结成夫妇，哈哈，让天下有情人终成眷属，岂非是最大的好事？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我们闲了这么多年，现在能为他们办办喜事，好好热闹一场，倒也开心得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已有二十多年没吃过喜酒了，这想必有趣得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "我就知道这小子没存好心，干的果然还是损人不利己的事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "替别人做媒，正是天大的好事，连阎王知道了，都要添我一纪阳寿，你怎么还说这不是好事呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你明知这两人现在都很伤心，却偏偏要他们现在成亲，这岂非比杀他们更缺德。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "他们就算现在很伤心，一尝到成亲后那种妙不可言的滋味，我保险他们绝不会再伤心了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "这条狗嘴里真是连一根象牙都吐不出来。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就叫狗改不了吃屎，坏蛋永远做不了好人的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不管你们怎么说，反正是非要这两人成亲不可的了。哈哈，我还要亲手替他们换上红衣裳，亲手替他们倒交杯酒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "这里反正还有一条母大虫，我们索性也替她找个老公吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，不错，这两人正是天生的一对。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这位大嫂子福气不差，也真和姓白的有缘，嫁来嫁去，都是姓白的，连姓都不必改了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "你们……你们……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "这是天大的喜事，你为什么还想溜呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你溜也溜不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道还有两个人要成亲，既是喜事，索性大家合在一起办吧，既省钱，又热闹。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你说的是那慕容家的小丫头和你那黑小子朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "慕容家的人，怎么会和咱们一齐办喜事呢？这赌鬼发疯了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们何必跟他们商量，到了那时候，我们就一齐拥进喜堂，将三对新人排在一起，再吃他们一顿喜酒，他们还能在好日子里跟我们翻脸么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好主意，好主意，哈哈，我们就跟他来个霸王硬上弓。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真希望他们酒席上有道菜是用人肉做的，到时你们吃你们的山珍海味，我也有人肉吃，那就真的皆大欢喜了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只望那天燕南天也去喝喜酒才好。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕南天绝不会到那里喝喜酒的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你怎么知道？你又不是他肚子里的蛔虫。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "燕南天现在一心只想找小鱼儿，哪有工夫去喝喜酒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你莫忘了，要找人一定会往人多的地方去找，办喜酒的地方人最多，我要是燕南天，也会去凑热闹的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "你龟儿子也莫忘了，现在替燕南天带路的人是谁。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在替燕南天带路的是江玉郎。江玉郎非但绝不会将燕南天带到慕容家去，也不会将燕南天带到人多的地方，他怕别人揭穿他的把戏。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "如此说来，岂非人越多的地方反而越安全？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最安全的地方，就是慕容家那些姑娘们的所在之地。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "一点也不错，想不到这赌鬼近来也变得聪明了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，我们现在还等什么，赶快走吧！哈哈，我这人天生就喜欢热闹，人越多越好。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    }
  ],
